{"tid":1925853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部發言人趙立堅 被發現Twitter追蹤蒼井空","createTime":"2020-03-14T16:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T23:37:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"faccf1df0699fb5ac99802dd6731595de043f3fb","tid":1925853,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8lKdXLf5V97at4iBeJmGmA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi40/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/a2evbGLAcAan2nmivPYOgg--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/f05816da87c9c5b8648a9602f9ca8d15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8lKdXLf5V97at4iBeJmGmA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi40%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fa2evbGLAcAan2nmivPYOgg--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Ff05816da87c9c5b8648a9602f9ca8d15&h=1505248c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/UrL2d2B.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部新任發言人趙立堅（圖），被網友發現推特帳號追蹤日本知名前AV女優蒼井空。（翻攝自@zlj517推特）<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部近來風波不斷，先是發言人華春瑩被發現翻牆給「習近平下台」的貼文按讚，如今又傳出新任發言人趙立堅推特帳號追蹤日本知名前AV女優蒼井空，再度引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅推特帳號成立將近9年，擁有25萬粉絲追蹤，由於他經常透過推特回應中國議題，有著「網紅發言人」「戰狼外交官」的稱號。本月24日，趙立堅以新任發言人的身分首度在例行記者會亮相，由華春瑩親自介紹給媒體。<br />\n<br />\n但趙立堅上任第二天，就被網友發現其推特帳號追蹤了日本前AV女優蒼井空。儘管目前趙立堅已取消追蹤，但截圖持續網路上被瘋傳。截至目前為止，中國官方或趙立堅本人都未針對此事做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部新任發言人趙立堅，被網友發現推特帳號追蹤日本知名前AV女優蒼井空。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國大陸網友紛紛表示「小趙本色演出！」「蒼井空是世界的！」「中國外交部真是人才濟濟」「能不能不要那麼露骨，改名援交部比較合理。」"},{"pid":"926cd9e8cd7c69119a1931188d1a7c00a56dde70","tid":1925853,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"蒼老師"},{"pid":"b6e0e1ae49825175f0028e1e1935d8039604098f","tid":1925853,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfd2265486725c379a7f95647218e1987e30423","tid":1925853,"uid":226955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"戰狼外交官戀上日本鬼子了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f824f33426df4badbae29b59a3c362bb6c0bbd93","tid":1925853,"uid":210140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街"},{"pid":"53fa684b82ffa6697f749b3c1161cfe8105f938a","tid":1925853,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位朋友, 幫手發這個聯署出去, 幫手找人簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=52b9d5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a><br />\n這個聯署是請求白宮要求youtube解釋為什麼限制談及武漢肺炎的題目? 為什麼限制言論自由? 希望大家幫手發出去, 因為被黃標了, 會影響收入, 是中共打壓言論自由的手段之一, 不可以就這樣被人打壓"},{"pid":"31325fee9f69b92aff9beae6a3b8d479414b71d6","tid":1925853,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"忍辱負重接近日本鬼子收集情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf3c4efbac48596b11f372043f6499158695f87","tid":1925853,"uid":303764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17